{"tid":1549770,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日美領毋需捉鬼，美國醒過你地，你估派鬼搞事美國自己唔知","createTime":"2019-09-07T12:31:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T03:59:48.000Z","uid":33307,"like":148,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"ac4663ee76f98538e85ba88aa2308fd1c8db13c2","tid":1549770,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:31:17.000Z","msg":"有人衝擊，只需要離開幾步，睇下佢做咩<br />\n最後就做返個證人，上黎起返係邊個POPO，話返比全世界知就ok<br />\n就ok<br />\n<br />\n千萬唔好同鬼打交<br />\n或者鬧佢<br />\n「群眾對群眾」既畫面係最最最柒<br />\n<br />\n鬼呢樣野，大家要輕鬆應對<br />\n以上建議只限美領範圍<br />\n其餘地方要多謝鬼帶頭（如果有）"},{"pid":"0e3e2ee3f5fc340a68dd5ad2b99af5364db68f01","tid":1549770,"uid":123991,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:31:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bb88621549957ccdf0a0296ec1e944558eefa818","tid":1549770,"uid":70524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:31:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d0c6b8f5cb5b3d1969781d41c844028c220434f9","tid":1549770,"uid":188337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:32:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"104e865b342ef5d0f0aeb9ec8004dff79da7c409","tid":1549770,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:35:05.000Z","msg":"麻煩幫手置頂1/10"},{"pid":"b3b6a894f320f7c1178ac54129413480b2916fc7","tid":1549770,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:37:13.000Z","msg":"麻煩幫手置頂2/10"},{"pid":"fde1c27e92741410cdfa3fe17b134c25e819134e","tid":1549770,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:37:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7bf38a03b429cd4018e62f4b0630d7f2345ccde","tid":1549770,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:38:21.000Z","msg":"麻煩幫手置頂3/10"},{"pid":"e5c64a248c675d6d4c5594ee102a33156d5e4cff","tid":1549770,"uid":22607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:38:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7ac6163c0badb56ac8484ffd857eb826a71ef7ce","tid":1549770,"uid":26876,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:38:53.000Z","msg":"借之前一個巴打寫嘅文一用<br />\n<br />\n佢哋大搖大擺行出警察宿舍，<br />\n每一個警察行過，都陰陰嘴笑鳩你班香港人：<br />\n「光復香港喎，時代革命喎。」<br />\n「曱甴。」<br />\n<br />\n每一個圍過警署嘅街坊，<br />\n都要接受依一班警察，<br />\n仲有佢哋家屬嘅冷眼。<br />\n「嗰隻甴曱啊，」佢指住你，<br />\n「嗰日佢咪圍鳩咗喺到囉，<br />\n依家咪死狗咁。」<br />\n<br />\n你忍唔住，你屌鳩佢老母。<br />\n不過佢一啲都無怕過你，<br />\n「甴曱！收皮啦！你打鳩我啊？！」<br />\n佢行埋嚟，再摸下你個頭，<br />\n「戇鳩仔。」<br />\n你忍住，你知道你唔可能打返佢。<br />\n佢拍拍你塊臉，<br />\n「點啊？你唔打鳩我喇？」<br />\n佢一啲收手嘅意欲都無，<br />\n因為警察已經為所欲為：<br />\n「又話黑警死全家？我全家仲喺到喎。」<br />\n<br />\n宿舍隔離就係警署，<br />\n警察一嚟到就會將你搭入去。<br />\n無人知道裏面會發生咩事。<br />\n你可能會畀人打一身、<br />\n畀人彈春袋、玩屎忽。<br />\n你女朋友喺你隔離，<br />\n你唔知道佢畀人拉埋入去之後會發生咩事，<br />\n你保護唔到你女朋友。<br />\n<br />\n「我要你同我道歉。」<br />\n警察一家望實你，同你講。<br />\n你唔敢再生事端。<br />\n「對唔住，好對唔住。」<br />\n最後你向警察道歉。<br />\n佢一邊拍你塊臉，一邊同你講，<br />\n「下次唔好喇。」<br />\n你覺得好興幸，<br />\n警察肯原諒你。<br />\n<br />\n依一個就係香港人放棄嘅結局，<br />\n你班「曱甴」依家想放棄未？"},{"pid":"e19a041fc26936a37bf92bbc39a16e4eaf5f0ef0","tid":1549770,"uid":58515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:39:04.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"b8d7ff4df2913f5643b818220a6502bdcb699e5b","tid":1549770,"uid":258592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:39:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c46f07e42ec8b75299eea6fc07a70e1ad934661","tid":1549770,"uid":20076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:40:11.000Z","msg":"收到VP"},{"pid":"538215eef34419ab5b97f0523e35128c61d81971","tid":1549770,"uid":33307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:42:11.000Z","msg":"最正係PoPo做鬼影晒比美國知道，諗起都射晒精"},{"pid":"67ef87914eded1359843d82ae89dd141e9005e03","tid":1549770,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c46f07e42ec8b75299eea6fc07a70e1ad934661","tid":1549770,"uid":20076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:40:11.000Z","msg":"收到VP"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:43:27.000Z","msg":"醒目仔"},{"pid":"9c774d7abd32a5c6a9a26054efe8c2539f8bdefd","tid":1549770,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:46:15.000Z","msg":"麻煩幫手置頂4/10"},{"pid":"2bac4268cdfd2ca95f5e4e1686519e341ff55df6","tid":1549770,"uid":58552,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:46:23.000Z","msg":"好歡迎黑警做鬼衝美領<br />\n畀美軍就地正法 射殺 我拍手"},{"pid":"fff2a6e4a2f2c4209485fc0e92017596de4bfea7","tid":1549770,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2bac4268cdfd2ca95f5e4e1686519e341ff55df6","tid":1549770,"uid":58552,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:46:23.000Z","msg":"好歡迎黑警做鬼衝美領<br />\n畀美軍就地正法 射殺 我拍手"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:47:15.000Z","msg":"支持POPO，絕不捉鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdeb7433ac21f9c5054e1e9e6c914db6a5a4f90f","tid":1549770,"uid":303110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2bac4268cdfd2ca95f5e4e1686519e341ff55df6","tid":1549770,"uid"